<plot>A young man silently drifts through the daily routine waiting for his life to begin. An old man hears fatal news and wonders what his life has meant. The paths of these two men cross when a heart attack strikes the old man as he exits the hospital parking ramp and the young man working the parking ramp booth at the exit becomes the only man who can come to the dying man's aid.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?063277</url></doc>
